descripctionAbout: Conquer Building Care Inc. is a commercial and residential cleaning company based in Miami, Florida. They offer a wide range of cleaning and maintenance services for businesses, specializing in detailed, high-quality solutions. Founded in 2017, it is led by Jose Roa, who serves as president. The company stands out for its focus on customer satisfaction and commitment to excellence. In addition to cleaning services, they also carry out interior and exterior painting and finishing projects, being specialists in the latter.
